data.title: generate your custom lyrics for the song
data.meta_description: Generate your own custom lyrics for Shirley Ellis' The Name Game and learn the rules. It's easy! So let's do Gary:  Gary, Gary, bo-bary, Banana-fana fo-fary.
data.text:
The Name Game - Lyrics Generator

The 'The Name Game - Lyrics Generator' generates you the custom lyrics/verse for Shirley Ellis' song 'The Name Game' with your name.

Just type in your name and you will get your very own lyrics to sing along.
